inputFormat:
The first line of the input contains exactly six integers $ n,k,l,r,s_{all},s_{k} $ ( $ 1<=n,k,l,r<=1000 $ ; $ l<=r $ ; $ k<=n $ ; $ 1<=s_{k}<=s_{all}<=10^{6} $ ).

It's guaranteed that the input is such that the answer exists.
outputFormat: Print exactly $ n $ integers $ a_{1},a_{2},...,a_{n} $ — the number of points each student scored. If there are multiple solutions, you can print any of them. You can print the distribution of points in any order.
translation: Valera 爱编程比赛，他参加了一场比赛。这场比赛有 $n$ 个选手参加，每个选手的分数至少为 $l$ 分，至多为 $r$ 分，所有选手分数总和为 $s_{all}$，并且分数前 $k$ 大的选手的分数和为 $s_k$，请输出满足条件的所有选手的分数（顺序无所谓）。
